<item>
            <title>[HBASE-9756] HBase shell help info would be better to display only when usage error instead of any exception</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9756</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When error occurred in HBase shell, no matter what error it is, the help info will display. As help info is used to instruct how to use the command, so it would be better to show help info only when the command is used in a wrong way.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
